cs.PL, cs.AR, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the semantics of transactions and weak memory models in programming languages and architectures, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL), architecture (cs.AR), logic in computer science (cs.LO), software engineering (cs.SE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper presents formal models and automated tooling for validating and checking TM-related transformations, which are typical topics in these sub-categories.
